  "detailed_description": "Welcome to the world of Sequential Dungeon, where 64 different levels in 8 uniquely themed worlds await you in a simple yet challenging experience! Get ready to bring your puzzle solving skills up to the task as there will be a limited amount of moves available to clear each of the levels, and with a vast array of different mechanics for you to master, it surely will not be an easy task!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368310/extras/a3d4e6aa24a0b0a7f44a22413df959d8.avif?t=1712050474\" width=612 height=70 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Explore 8 uniquely themed floors</li><li>Solve 64 challenging puzzles, or skip them if they prove too challenging</li><li>Experience 14 easy to understand yet challenging mechanics</li><li>Easy to understand gameplay with challenging puzzles</li></ul>",
